<p><a href="#sdfootnote20anc" name="sdfootnote20sym">20</a> Zob. m.in. Françoise Lionnet, <em>Autobiographical Voices: Race, Gender, Self-Portraiture</em>, Cornell University Press, Ithaca 1989; <em>Women, Autobiography, Theory: A Reader</em>, red. S. Smith, J. Watson, University of Wisconsin Press, Madison 1998; <em>Interfaces: Women, Autobiography, Image, Performance</em>, red. S. Smith, J. Watson, University of Michigan Press, Ann Arbor 2002.</p>
